HubContent:665f414ea2cbaa0024d957dd.desc: "Join us in Barcelona for Unite 2024 on September 18–20 – our biggest Unite in years.\n\n"
HubContent:65cbce3d881c3300244a1321.desc: "Speed up prototyping and development with AI capabilities that answer your questions fast and generate unique assets and textures in-editor. "
HubContent:6357d6f576b6d4a055435ca6.desc: "Streamline development and add new features to your projects with quality tools and art from the Asset Store."
HubContent:65d64d8c535def0024b71c3f.desc: "Level up anywhere, any time, and at your own pace with hundreds of hours of training content designed to upskill professionals in any industry.\n\n"
HubContent:6357d6f576b6d4a055435c2c.desc: "Read it all here first. Don't miss the latest features, announcements, creator achievements, tips & tricks and so much more."
HubContent:6357d6f576b6d4a055435c1e.desc: "Beginners and experts alike contribute, helping each other with Unity. The built-in voting system points you to the best answers fast."
HubContent:6357d6f576b6d4a055435c23.desc: "Post questions, find answers, see awesome projects, meet your peers, or even find someone to help your project or your team."
HubContent:6357d6f576b6d4a055435c27.desc: "Want to provide feedback directly to the Unity teams? Join Unity Pulse, the community at the heart of building a better Unity."
HubContentCategory:636191e45917ba0025a98: "Tools to let you work together anywhere, anytime"
HubContent:636192165917ba0025a98909.desc: "Connect to your teammates anywhere with high-performance, low latency remote collaboration, so your team feels like they never left the office. Try for free."
HubContent:637e62b3e8afa600261c6ca6.desc: "Accelerate team review and collaboration for all types of media files including images, videos, 360-degree content, and 3D models. Try for free."
Template:com%2eunity%2etemplate%2euniver: "This is an empty project configured for 2D apps. It uses Unity’s Universal Render Pipeline pre-configured with 2D Renderer."

Template:com%2eunity%2etemplate%2eurp-bl: "The URP (Universal Render Pipeline) blank template includes the settings and assets you need to start creating with URP. Equipped with  artist-friendly workflows for both 3D and 2D based projects, URP allows for quick and easy iteration with optimised best-in-class graphics that range across a multitude of platforms from mobile to high-end consoles and PCs."

Template:com%2eunity%2etemplate%2ehdrp-b: "The HDRP (High Definition Render Pipeline) blank template includes the settings and assets you need to start creating with HDRP. Utilizing physically-based lighting techniques, offering advanced materials, lighting and post processing options, compatible with real-time Ray Tracing and offline pathtracing, and leveraging a configurable hybrid tile/cluster deferred/forward lighting architecture, HDRP gives you the tools you need to create projects at a high graphical standard for high end platforms (Windows, Linux, Mac, PS4, PS5, XBox One, Xbox Series, and Desktop VR)."
Template:com%2eunity%2etemplate%2eurp-sa: "These four environments showcase the versatility, scalability, and customizability of the Universal Render Pipeline (URP). The project demonstrates the wide range of URP 3D projects achievable, by presenting different art styles, rendering paths, and scene complexities, tailored for a wide range of platforms from mobile and untethered devices to high-end PCs and consoles."
